<script src="http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/respond.js/1.3.0/respond.js"></script>
<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
       

        <div class="col-lg-4" style="margin-top:50px;width:300px;float:left;margin-right:50px;">
            <div id="map-container"></div>

            <!-- jQuery (necessary for Bootstrap's JavaScript plugins) -->
            <script src="http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.0.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
            <!-- Include all compiled plugins (below), or include individual files as needed -->
            <script src="http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.1.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
            <script src="http://maps.google.com/maps/api/js?sensor=false"></script>
            <script>


      function init_map() {
          var var_location = new google.maps.LatLng(43.84864, 18.35644);

        var var_mapoptions = {
          center: var_location,
          zoom: 14
        };

		var var_marker = new google.maps.Marker({
			position: var_location,
			map: var_map,
			title:"Sarajevo"});

        var var_map = new google.maps.Map(document.getElementById("map-container"),
            var_mapoptions);

		var_marker.setMap(var_map);

      }

      google.maps.event.addDomListener(window, 'load', init_map);

            </script>

        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4" style="margin-top:50px;width:700px;">
            We like printing, we have been doing it for a while now and we like to think we are pretty good at it. We offer all the usual things you would expect, high quality products and great customer service. But rather than get the loudhailer out and make a sales pitch, we prefer a more relaxed approach.

            So we are here to help whatever your printing needs. The big thing that makes us ‘special’ is that we do offer a genuine next day delivery option. Order by 1pm, we’ll dispatch same day for next day delivery to mainland UK addresses.

            It’s really that simple. We saw an opportunity to provide a wide product range as standard while remaining flexible to individual needs, creating bespoke printing on request.

            We have worked with great companies along the way, including the BBC, Barclays and the NHS. There is no resting on our laurels though; we follow a kiazen philosophy, always seeking to improve our service and products, whilst having a smile on our face at the same time.
        </div>

        </div>

    </div>

